destroy table inet codestead_runner_guest
add table inet codestead_runner_guest
add chain inet codestead_runner_guest input { type filter hook input priority filter; policy drop; }
add chain inet codestead_runner_guest output { type filter hook output priority filter; policy accept; }
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input ct state invalid drop
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input iifname "lo" accept
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input ct state established,related accept
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input ip saddr 192.168.122.1 tcp dport 22 accept
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input ip saddr 192.168.122.1 tcp dport 4100 accept
add rule inet codestead_runner_guest input ip saddr 172.29.40.2 tcp dport 4100 accept
